			<div class="content" id="post-content-2462757">
									

<p>Relevant reading! <a href="/scp-2474">SCP-2474</a>. :D</p>
<p>So&#8230; wow. This took <em>a lot</em> of time to write, research, discuss, etc.</p>
<p>Anyway, this is for the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/mobile-task-force-contest">MTF contest</a>! Many, many thanks to the Notos team members <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1456355504" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/von-pincier" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1315056); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1315056&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1456355504" alt="Von Pincier" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1315056)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/von-pincier" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1315056); return false;">Von Pincier</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1456355504" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span> for so, so much help with character discussion, detail nitpicking, and overall inspiration. (Kalinin helped <em>a lot</em> with the dialogue.)</p>
<p>I consulted a handwriting analysis book for the notes. Took me many, many tries. All the images in the tale belong to me, except for the dagger belonging to Pang, which is licensed under Wikimedia Commons. <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">yes I have a lot of weird stuff lying around, I am a total packrat</span></p>
<p>What happens when you're an AI hiding out on a gigantic spaceship, and your team can't talk to you?</p>

