														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2465140">
									

<p>Wow, this was a really neat tale, as you not only provided great characterization of the other members of the MTF, but Manu as well. Additionally, the mixed media really helps this tale succeed in building that &quot;Diary&quot; feel.</p>
<p>I will say that while Manu's learning and observations are adorable, they also strike me as being kind of creepy. This is mainly due to the fact that these people are being watched around the clock largely without their knowledge (maybe). I fear that Manu might let it slip that what was observed was something private and have it blow up in the poor AI's face.</p>
<p>Either way, looking forward to what ever is next.</p>
<p>+1.</p>

